j4AgRYmpqgykw">Hồ Nguyên Trừng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/Th%E1%BA%A5t-nguy%E1%BB%87t-th%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BA%ADt-ng%E1%BB%99-m%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A2n-k%E1%BB%B5-nh%E1%BA%ADt-c%E1%BA%A3m-t%C3%A1c/poem-9TJAZk7k01FEGFa-jBQG6g">Thất nguyệt thất thập nhật ngộ mẫu thân kỵ nhật cảm tác - 七月七十日遇母親忌日感作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nho-Ho%C3%A0n/author-pEICBCCrXfpItm0RL1cOfw">Đinh Nho Hoàn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-%C4%90i%E1%BB%81n-t%E1%BB%A9-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n-Qu%E1%BB%B3-Ch%C3%A2u-B%C3%A1-trung-th%E1%BB%ABa-m%E1%BB%87nh-kh%E1%BB%9Fi-c%C6%B0-Giang-L%C4%83ng-ti%E1%BA%BFt-%C4%91%E1%BB%99-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%C3%A0nh-qu%E1%BA%ADn/poem-KCSp53jkU2KJKEY4FwLafw">Tống Điền tứ đệ tướng quân Quỳ Châu Bá trung thừa mệnh khởi cư Giang Lăng tiết độ Dương Thành quận vương Vệ công mạc - 送田四弟將軍夔州柏中丞命起居江陵節度陽城郡王衛公幕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BB%B1-Nguy%C3%AAn/T%E1%BB%91ng-nh%C3%A2n-qu%C3%A1-V%E1%BB%87-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-jNrpfY5hBBOq5b27DwPecg">Tống nhân quá Vệ Châu - 送人過衛州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-C%E1%BB%B1-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-ujv3_N4k0KkIvWqK4PUlgw">Dương Cự Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-V%C4%83n-Ngh%E1%BB%8B-I/Xu%C3%A2n/poem-gsX9TXNMbD65I1KsjpT4oA">Xuân - 春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-V%C4%83n-Ngh%E1%BB%8B-I/author-j2yv60iLSGVWsUs_D51NxQ">Phạm Văn Nghị (I)</a>)<br></div>	</div>
